CS350 Assignment #4 - Multithreading Reader/Writer Problem - Writer Preference
Daniel Bottcher & Matthew Van Gorden
dbottch1 & mvangor3

Makefile: 
    make/make all: generates readwrite executable and main.o file

    make clean: removes all output (reader_#.txt) files, object files, and executable from directory 

Usage: 
readwrite <Number of reads/writes per thread> <Number of reader threads> <Number of Writer threads>

Ex: ./readwrite 40 3 7


